==================================================================\
Stash the uncommitted changes\
git stash list (This will give list of stashes with Id)\
git stash save \'93Title\'94 (This will create the stash copy of uncommitted changes)\
git stash apply stashId (This will apply the stash to the current branch. Current stash will stay in stash list)\
git stash drop stashId (This will remove the stash from stash list)\
git stash pop stashId (This will apply the stash to the current branch. And remove the stash from stash list)\
git stash show -p stashId (This will show the files with changes which were stored in that stash)\
